page.title: 06DUKE OF WELLINGTON
page.content: The Duke of Wellington was 83 years old when he died.Wellington had 67,000 men and 156 guns.Napoleons army numbered 74,000 men and 246 guns.There is a {WELLINGTON COUNTRY PARK }and a Wellington {"STRATFIELD SAYE"}House near {BRAMLEY.}The Duke of Wellington owned most of{STRATFIELD SAYE.} These are the words that were written on the Duke of Wellington's grave: {THE CHARGER RIDDEN BY THE DUKE OF {WELLINGTON THE ENTIRE DAY AT THE {BATTLE OF WATERLOO.BORN 1808 DIED 1836 The Wellington house was smaller than The Vyne.The Duke of Wellington still owns Purdues Farm but recently he sold half to Mr.Best.
